    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Guns are Funs” 是一款结合了射击、跑酷和摧毁塔楼元素的街机游戏。沉浸在玩具士兵的世界中，他们在房间内激烈地争夺权力和影响力。激动人心的动态战斗、独特的任务和各种游戏模式等着您。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003640/extras/42be2c9f53f91771ee743830474ac093.poster.avif?t=1765388092\" width=356 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003640/extras/42be2c9f53f91771ee743830474ac093.webm?t=1765388092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003640/extras/42be2c9f53f91771ee743830474ac093.mp4?t=1765388092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事活动分为几个章节，每个章节都提供不同的任务，挑战您在游戏不同方面的技能。如果您正在寻找一些没有叙事的不间断乐趣，请进入沙盒模式 - 您可以在其中探索所有游戏元素并争夺最高分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003640/extras/fd5bf1e002fa2eb7993396d7bd3b8d21.poster.avif?t=1765388092\" width=356 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003640/extras/fd5bf1e002fa2eb7993396d7bd3b8d21.webm?t=1765388092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003640/extras/fd5bf1e002fa2eb7993396d7bd3b8d21.mp4?t=1765388092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建您的玩具军队，摧毁敌人的塔楼，并证明即使是最小的士兵也可以成为最伟大的英雄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生动的 3D 图形</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >激动人心和有趣的情节</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漫画过场动画</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的游戏模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作者的音乐伴奏</p></li></ul>",
